title: >>> RUMORS Welcome
body_text:
"RUMORS Welcome" is back on this March day, in preparation for the 32nd installment of dodgeball.
I.
Tom Adams has decided to only play at events ending in 2, 5, and 8.
II.
If there is a small turnout similarly to XXX-ONE, then "Prison Ball" could very well take place.
III.
Steve Adams is expected to make his return ... at DODGEBALL 33. He will be missing 32 due to a dental surgery.
IV.
Dan Spengeman made the DODGEBALL 32 poster.
DODGEBALL 32 is this Saturday night and what an event it is going to be. Spring has arrived, but will the weather see a drastic change?
Check back in the days to come for more on DODGEBALL 32!
